quote.summary: C-Link Squared Limited is a Malaysia-based investment holding company. The Company and its subsidiaries are principally engaged in the provision of outsourced services, including the provision of outsourced document management services and related software applications and enterprise software solutions services in Malaysia as well as the provision of outsourced insurance risk analysis services and insurance marketing services in the People's Republic of China (PRC), and the distribution and sales of medical equipment in the PRC. Its services include electronic document delivery, document print and mail fulfillment, magnetic ink character recognition (MICR) cheque print and mail fulfillment, medical identity (ID) card print and mail fulfillment, and document imaging and scanning services.
